net.hudup.core.evaluate

Class RealMetricValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.evaluate.RealMetricValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, MetricValue

    public class RealMetricValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements MetricValue
    This abstract class represents a single number as a MetricValue. Note, MetricValue interface represents value of a metric, which can be anything. Therefore, this class is the simplest implementation of MetricValue.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
    See Also:
